    <exercise>
      <statement>
        <p>
          The Colonel spots a campfire at a of bearing N<m>42^{\circ}</m>E from his current position.
          Sarge, who is positioned 3000 feet due east of the Colonel,
          reckons the bearing to the fire to be N<m>20^{\circ}</m>W from his current position.
